title: Ample Parking with Garage Parking Available, Poolside Lounge
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 7', 'OR Text', '7', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 773 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Woods of Burnsville Apartments offer the best value in apartment living in the Burnsville, Minnesota area.', 'We are committed to your comfort and convenience.', 'Enjoy prompt service from our professional staff, and benefit from our extraordinary community features including a resident clubhouse with a 24-hour fitness center, sparkling swimming pool, sports courts, and more!', 'Choose from newly renovated spacious studio, 1, 2 or 3 bedroom apartment homes with amenities including private decks and patios, walk-in closets, and modern interior finishes.', 'Our apartment homes are located in a park-like setting, yet just minutes from the Twin Cities.', 'With convenient access to I-35 you can get where you need to be easily.', 'Enjoy great shopping, dining, and entertainment all within a short ride.', "With a full range of luxury amenities and premier location, you'll feel right at home.", 'Features:', 'Wood Finish Flooring (In Select Units), Energy-Efficient Air Conditioning & Heat, Ceiling Fans, Garbage Disposal, Microwave, Pantries & Extra Storage Closets, Balcony or Patio, Dishwasher, Walk-in Closets (In Select Units)', 'Community Amenities:', 'Poolside Lounge, 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Team, Clubhouse, Sports Courts, Barbecue Grills with Picnic Tables, Apple Valley High School, Controlled Access Buildings, Laundry Facility, Valley Middle School, Scenic views, Ample Parking with Garage Parking Available, Fitness Center, Large Trees and Park-Like Landscaping, Resident Portal, Southview Elementary School, Sparkling Swimming Pool, On-Site Management with High Service Standards', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', '4XGeqXLgteB']
